{
  "id": "RAW_b0c43cd1",
  "title": "2 张 A800，让大模型跑 1 亿上下文！陈天桥旗下团队联合北大狠作：直接把记忆写进注意力机制！记忆和推理完美解耦了！网友：优雅！RAG 真完了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODI5Njc2MA==&mid=2655937322&idx=1&sn=1306a94cebac0f435a972781f604a51b",
  "date": "2026-03-20 04:34:00",
  "author": "51CTO技术栈",
  "siteName": "51CTO技术栈",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453671\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" type=\"block\" data-ratio=\"0.42592592592592593\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a76bf682&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgL3dNY6icVmX8kqnIJphjiaOEBeUicdY1ia6J7zkRzKZtObmVIVhYIAhDd5sS1BevtMT8TsFmV6LBkC8fqKEvdqNoJhQnxBum2xBR0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; text-align: center;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: #888888;\">编辑 | 云昭</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"77\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">逆天！仅需 2 张 A800 就能驱动 1 亿 Token 的推理！</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那个曾经的“中国首富”陈天桥，带着他在脑科学与 AI 领域的野心重回大模型战场了！</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"6\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就在最近，盛大集团旗下的&nbsp;</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"27\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Evermind</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;团队联合北京大学发表了一篇相当炸裂的论文：</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"63\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">MSA（Memory Sparse Attention）</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453670\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.7208121827411168\" data-w=\"591\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9e68c4e6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgI2NyvsRUwm1NibNrDHIB8eSKHO0QayKicicIP0iaJTNEt1tW1lBeS3FibZe2WRIgpeFQn2FH0PPEkjtTU6CqWibZCGP59Er7D3J1daY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"7\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这篇论文的核心目标只有一个：捅破“LLM 推理上下文”的天花板，</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"14\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">让 AI 拥有“一生”的记忆。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453664\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.5145631067961165\" data-w=\"927\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=648d2f1e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgLYfqMPruuxM0VCyzzX3rURKgXx7kticqDhuJOjnicVlH1VxX4MekTUvkHf85U97B6flfJJR7Ricl4oSpUJYoEDLYic3CCaJHJ3ia8Y%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"7\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"14\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">“百万上下文”是当前大模型的“死亡线”</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如今的大模型，依旧存在不小的\"金鱼记忆\"困境，即最前沿的 LLM 有效上下文，只有128K 到1M token，再长就会“胡言乱语”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">虽然这相较于三年前的模型有很大的改进，但相较于人而言，还差得很远。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">人类一生可以积累数亿 tokens 的信息记忆，而最先进的大模型，通常只能处理&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;10 万到 100 万 tokens。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"444\" data-end=\"464\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这里的差距，不是几倍，而是</span></span><strong data-start=\"454\" data-end=\"463\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">两个数量级</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。更关键的是，这种“短记忆”正在卡住下一阶段的AI：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"500\" data-end=\"518\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无法真正读完一整套小说并持续理解</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"521\" data-end=\"550\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无法维持一个长期稳定的人格（Digital Twin）</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"553\" data-end=\"576\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无法支撑一个有“历史”的 Agent 持续决策</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"578\" data-end=\"583\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">换句话说：AI已经很聪明了，但它记不住“来时路”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"578\" data-end=\"583\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: #0080ff;font-weight: bold;\">为什么从百万到一亿token的上下文跨越，很难？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"614\" data-end=\"634\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而过去几年，行业其实一直在“补这个洞”：最开始是用 RAG 把知识“外挂”进来，后来是用各种长上下文模型硬撑，要么就是 Agent 拆分上下文运行。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"578\" data-end=\"583\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但问题也很明显。论文指出，暴力扩窗口的做法的核心挑战在于，传统的 Full Attention 具有&nbsp;</span></span><span data-math=\"O(L^2)\" data-index-in-node=\"22\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">O(L^2)</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;的复杂度，随着 Token 长度（L）增加，计算量和显存占用呈指数级爆炸。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"6\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">即便引入了 GQA（分组查询注意力）或 FlashAttention，处理超过 100 万 Token 时，KV Cache 的膨胀依然会让最顶级的 H100 集群感到窒息。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那么MSA是如何解决这一难题的呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"6\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">2张显卡跑1亿长度的秘密</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"6\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;MSA 的底层逻辑：把记忆直接写进注意力</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与外挂 RAG、外推上下文的做法不同，论文提出了一种&nbsp;</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"0\" data-index-in-node=\"12\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">MSA（Memory Sparse Attention，存储稀疏注意力）</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;的系统架构，从算法优化、位置编码、工程并行三个维度，解决了大模型处理“一生长度”（1亿 Tokens）信息的瓶颈。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453654\" data-ratio=\"0.17899761336515513\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"838\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f871c7fe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgLa7vmXXaDl47J3MOicWkd9Y2niaHtMjUYHm5E2f5vNs06MjeqO8mUibDONeQqibcH76jxLqVt4lQibNEnuR58E0FWkHspjFcrXQD2s%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">具体有四个技术亮点：</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"2\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">1. 从“死记硬背”转向“精准打捞”：稀疏检索机制</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"3\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">传统模型（如 GPT-4）像是在看书时试图同时盯着所有页码，文字越多，眼睛越不够用。MSA 则像是一个带着</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"53\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">索引目录</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">的超级大脑：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"4,0,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"4,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">潜空间路由（Latent Routing）：</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;MSA 引入了专门的 Router（路由投影器）。它不是在文本层级检索，而是在模型的隐藏状态（潜空间）中，通过计算 Query 与 KV Cache（存储块）之间的余弦相似度，像雷达一样瞬间定位出最相关的 Top-k 个文档。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">KV 缓存压缩：</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;它将海量文档切成固定长度的分块，并进行“均值池化”压缩。这样即使背景资料高达一亿 Token，模型需要实时处理的数据量也被大幅削减，从而保证了极低的推理延迟。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Zhxqo7xEfgKb27Bic2GNW0iao15HpEYc85osgAwWHdPe3uZFMO2lYfSsM3mapyvM2U5UvSlUOBSfjg1681WLpMTJdyHYBFQRxGuUJMsmg5Nws/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1002\" data-cropy2=\"490.30249110320284\" data-imgfileid=\"508453656\" data-ratio=\"0.48902195608782434\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1002\" style=\"width: 562px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7e496fe0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZhxqo7xEfgKlWic9NT2amIBw88CU3ibefnzexPUS1ERl8yTm65K8hNyXcS8Zn5yicV1IFbQ78n1hTG3GLJfELueYq2icah3w1wN0PuUVxWgsoqM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"5\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">2. 解决“时空错乱”：独立文档位置编码 (Doc-wise RoPE)</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"6\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">处理一亿长度最大的敌人是</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"12\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">位置偏移</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。如果按照传统做法从第 1 编号到第 1 亿，模型在推理时会因为位置太远而“大脑宕机”。</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">位置脱钩：</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;MSA 为每一个存入记忆的文档分配独立的、从 0 开始的位置 ID。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">逻辑延续：</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;无论你存了多少文档，模型感知到的永远是局部的、高精度的语义关联。这让模型在仅用短文本训练的情况下，具备了向一亿长度无损“外推”的能力，解决了训练与推理长度不匹配的沉疴。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"8\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">3. 模拟“联想思考”：记忆交织 (Memory Interleave)</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"9\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人脑在回忆一生往事时，往往是“想到一点，再联想出另一点”。</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">多步推理：</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;MSA 提出“存储交织”机制。模型可以先检索出一部分记忆，经过思考后，再根据产生的中间结论发起第二次、第三次针对性检索。这种“检索-思考-再检索”的闭环，让它能处理分布在不同年份、不同文档里的碎片化信息，完成复杂的多跳逻辑推理。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453657\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.47953216374269003\" data-w=\"1026\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f3cad32f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgLOLbneTh2YHRRRsGwzsS04mQJN2HbkAIADKFhE0LhR0qibQrnCjUCvzTa1r3SuwHwIvMRaEqQdR57EZZThp42UjiaYVhZrxZ5xs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"11\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">4. 暴力美学的工程实现：内存并行 (Memory Parallel)</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"12\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一亿 Token 的 KV 缓存如果全塞进显存，需要天文数字般的硬件。研究团队开发了一种内存并行技术，将海量记忆分布式存储在多台设备或系统内存中。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"12\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">使得模型的部署硬件门槛降低到了“平民级”。</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"17\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">仅需 2 张 NVIDIA A800 GPU</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，就能驱动一亿 Token 的实时推理。这让“一生长度”的记忆不再是大厂独占的军备竞赛。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">总结下，通过以上对传统注意力机制“手术”，MSA 让模型学会了「挑重点看」，复杂度下降到了</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;O(L) 线性级别，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">1亿token上下文，2张A800就能跑。同时，实现表示，上下文推理窗口实现了</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">16K→1亿token，而且精度衰减 &lt;9%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 4 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">结果：4B模型击败 GPT-4、Qwen-235B RAG系统</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-index-in-node=\"8\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">研究团队专门为 MSA 做了一场可扩展实验。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-index-in-node=\"8\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">数据结果非常震撼：</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"14\" data-pm-slice=\"2 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">仅有&nbsp;</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">4B 参数的 MSA</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">，在实际表现中竟然打赢了&nbsp;</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"43\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">235B 参数的巨型 RAG 系统</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">。这证明了：</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"66\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">原生的稀疏记忆，远比堆参数更高效。</span></span></b></b></b></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-index-in-node=\"8\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">在从 1.6 万到 1 亿 Token 的超长上下文跨度下，MSA 的性能损耗保持在 9% 以内。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453655\" data-ratio=\"0.509090909090909\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"660\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bea560d2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgIrpa8ibBMYiaZINhK89eCiaIgbPiabc9uWdqypFXybF9SLbI2j0PwoDJnS7a7nTAjvVibfxMM1UWv4CIKhUmJy6uice9jZC2SYmic0j0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">这</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一规模已接近人类一生长效记忆的预估容量。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比之下，传统的长文本模型（如 Qwen2.5-14B-1M、Qwen3-30B/80B-A3B）以及外部存储系统（如 MemAgent-14B）在这一量级下都会遭遇灾难性的性能崩溃。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"2\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与目前最先进的（SOTA）RAG 系统不同，MSA 无需复杂的检索管线和启发式超参数（如 Top-k 召回数量或相关性阈值）。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"2\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一能力的实现，标志着&nbsp;</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"75\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">LLM 记忆力与人类认知规模之间的差距正在被有效弥合</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，从而让那些此前被认为神经模型无法实现的实际应用场景成为可能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"14\" data-pm-slice=\"2 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-path-to-node&quot;:&quot;7&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"66\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">大海捞针、长上下文QA场景测试，得分亮眼</span></span></b></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"14\" data-pm-slice=\"2 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-path-to-node&quot;:&quot;7&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"66\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">一个显著的场景是，在大海捞针（NIAH）的测试中，在 1M Token 长度下，原始 Backbone（Qwen3-4B-Instuct） 的准确率会跌至惨不忍睹的 24.69%，而 MSA 依然稳在&nbsp;</span></span></b></b><b data-path-to-node=\"8,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"74\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">94.84%</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453659\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.4378698224852071\" data-w=\"1014\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=309b5439&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgIb4fYyS7miaBmrw4w98KibvIa9gqiaA7wqOUflnKtJfm9GPIJTaDPU1VCjlH1oB5tN4xUYY7W83tS4hVBQ8N1icriaNAcAw9NujibWU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">此外，在长上下文 QA 中，MSA 对于 RAG 系统也实现了吊打。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">在同等 Backbone 下，MSA 的得分比 RAG 高出&nbsp;</span></span></b><b data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"47\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">16%</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">；面对专业的 HippoRAG2，优势依然保持在&nbsp;</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"75\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">14.8%</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453663\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.31343283582089554\" data-w=\"1005\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1b9e462d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgKVFA9tKWKtBmRNfHJ0zWKX6QLJuP0SXOEE1IiarO63eoWMRYbFJTdlk9kJX47CVibNQNDylumc06tWom2vALuHhQyGkiaFXkXRXk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">同时别忘了，这里仅仅只用了 2 张 A800 ，在跑 1 亿 token 的推理任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">模型推理与“记忆容量”解耦</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">论文指出了一个重要的结论：MSA 实现了将模型的记忆容量与推理能力的解耦。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">“MSA 在长上下文基准测试中显著超越了前沿语言模型、最先进的 RAG 系统以及主流记忆型 Agent。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">这些结果表明，通过将“记忆容量”与“推理能力”解耦，MSA 为通用模型提供了一条可扩展的路径，使其具备内生的、生命周期级别的记忆能力。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: #0080ff;font-weight: bold;\">网友热议：比RAG优雅多了！</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">这篇文章在 X 上发布后，迅速斩获 40K+ 的围观。X 上不少人对此大为赞赏：</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"48\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">“优雅”</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453665\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"1.011037527593819\" data-w=\"453\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=feeb57a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgIgtdHJicTYcohRMFnenUHQv5ibCf8JhhDg30RHTRTcmouhGFsEUpkCpjMH72dRKP3NIkQCbficQAgc936mbjwiaef26WFGcXaFnAk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">一位网友表示：</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;“把检索直接做进 Attention 机制里，比 RAG 那种笨重的外挂方案优雅太多了。”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453653\" data-ratio=\"0.24503311258278146\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"453\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=abffa1e0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgKtDzOL9a81Ph40JSkHSlfs69wrvPYKUNuatNImlwOhSwIyEK5CznE2gDxUVQzPKl7a8JqDDsbHdzg5knCPI3Sm5eMUgKcPyOI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">甚至有网友设想， “如果这种架构普及，AI 真的可以达到‘真正理解’全领域论文的水平。”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453668\" data-ratio=\"0.28546712802768165\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"578\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4fdfcaa3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgKJEgRwGvUicsPvibSHaaKzkwHKLkDBUnRRiaQpgB7lSynhSwxzFjxpJAAic2qQwbP0yuiaRloCw3VicaqJywdvTeUQuoTPSeAVXHgicA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"13\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">当然，硬核推友们也提出了尖锐的</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"15\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">技术三连问</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"14,0,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">现有成熟的 Transformer 生态（如 HuggingFace）如何兼容这种底层修改？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"14,1,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">存量模型如何迁移？通过 LoRA 轻量化训练是否可行？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"14,1,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453666\" data-ratio=\"0.26262626262626265\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"594\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be2b7524&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgIvXjGxW1O9miaAkibx43IdstrNJIlVlX3FRVxbAOCfA9zuia9EUOumpicmHHxjiczagNMM75lQzGxBMPuZavn5eTmvL3Pjfpcdo6MU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"14,2,0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">还有网友往前想了一步：那之后，在企业级应用中，多租户的数据隔离和知识实时更新成本如何解决？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453669\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.211340206185567\" data-w=\"582\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5ad7c728&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgJwM3rjgR2n2BtiaB3ialyibqf1Yvaq6TZT0vqicuTr9Iziaz56fVIoB8xyhvPqebuQV1kj9jqOgPRjfvWkEiaPicOkTOr3VOj3XUxCGE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"14,2,0\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">但相信还有不少朋友会感叹大模型进展的速度：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"14,2,0\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">100 M上下文的问题如果解决了，基本上就没有人类什么事情了！</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"14,2,0\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">因为这几乎代表着可以把整个Linux内核代码直接输入，那么超大型软件工程、长篇小说作品，大模型也可以出色生成和维护了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508453667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.2205128205128205\" data-w=\"585\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=485f6fdd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZhxqo7xEfgJiaIMFzBK1ibrnQibyzTBd8KUP8DsjcBNr6XlMVoiaMBUbjrHMuI5SUl4TwtTCeHzax9H9XzRdY95P2o0GdIeylWQPPpMtqE47BPc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">从这个层面上看，不止 RAG 会“失业”，就连大家丢饭碗的节奏，又得加快一波了</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">（狗头）~</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">总之，大家在注意力机制上的研究，越来越热闹了！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: #888888;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: #888888;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/EverMind-AI/MSA\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/EverMind-AI/MSA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: #888888;\"><a href=\"https://evermind.ai/\" target=\"_blank\">https://evermind.ai/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: #888888;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/elliotchen100/status/2034479369855590660\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/elliotchen100/status/2034479369855590660</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "陈天桥旗下 Evermind 团队联合北大推出 MSA 架构，通过将检索集成进注意力机制，实现 2 张 A800 驱动 1 亿 token 超长上下文推理。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "陈天桥旗下 Evermind 团队联合北大推出 MSA 架构，通过将检索集成进注意力机制，实现 2 张 A800 驱动 1 亿 token 超长上下文推理。",
  "summary": "本文详细介绍了由 Evermind 团队与北京大学联合发表的突破性研究：存储稀疏注意力（MSA）。该技术旨在打破大语言模型在长上下文处理上的“百万代币”瓶颈，通过将记忆检索直接融入注意力机制，实现了记忆容量与推理能力的完美解耦。MSA 核心包含潜空间路由、独立文档位置编码、记忆交织及内存并行四大技术，将计算复杂度降至线性级别。实验证明，仅 4B 参数的 MSA 模型在长文本任务中表现优于 235B 的 RAG 系统，且硬件门槛极低，仅需两张 A800 显卡即可支持一亿 Token 的实时推理，为构建具备“一生记忆”的 AI 智能体提供了新路径。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "MSA 通过潜空间路由实现精准的稀疏检索机制。",
      "explanation": "引入专门的路由投影器在隐藏状态中计算相似度，像索引目录一样瞬间定位相关文档块，将注意力机制的复杂度从平方级降至线性级别。"
    },
    {
      "point": "采用独立文档位置编码解决了长序列的位置偏移难题。",
      "explanation": "为每个文档分配独立的起始位置 ID，实现位置脱钩，使模型在短文本训练下也能无损外推至亿级长度，解决了训练与推理长度不匹配的沉疴。"
    },
    {
      "point": "记忆交织机制模拟人类联想思考实现多步推理。",
      "explanation": "模型可先检索部分记忆并产生中间结论，再发起针对性检索，这种“检索-思考-再检索”的闭环使其能处理分布在不同文档中的碎片化信息。"
    },
    {
      "point": "MSA 实现了模型记忆容量与推理能力的有效解耦。",
      "explanation": "通过内存并行技术将海量 KV 缓存分布式存储，使小参数模型也能拥有巨大的内生记忆力，且在超长上下文下性能损耗保持在 9% 以内。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "MSA 的底层逻辑：把记忆直接写进注意力。",
    "仅有 4B 参数的 MSA，在实际表现中竟然打赢了 235B 参数的巨型 RAG 系统。",
    "MSA 实现了将模型的记忆容量与推理能力的解耦。",
    "把检索直接做进 Attention 机制里，比 RAG 那种笨重的外挂方案优雅太多了。",
    "仅需 2 张 NVIDIA A800 GPU，就能驱动一亿 Token 的实时推理。"
  ],
